name: aurora
description:
Fabulous organically faceted smokey quartz dangle from 14k gold-filled hoops. 

The smokey quartz of these earrings is a true translucent taupey shade of brown, it's been faceted in an erratic pattern, keeping with the natural shape of the stone.

These earrings measure 3" in length.

name: lucinda
description:
Clusters of faceted rock crystals adorn these layered 14k gold-filled hoops.

Each hoop is made from a single piece of gold wire hand-wrapped into a delicate loop.

Very simple, light, elegant, stunning.

name: novella
description:
Pink Opals on Gold

Genuine (not to mention large!) pale pink opals dangle from thick, multi-layered 14k gold-fill hoops.

To finish the design, a length of 14k gold-fill chain dangles from the front to the back of the earring. Just lovely.

All on 14k gold-fill materials.

name: amaranthia
description:
Tiffany Stone on Gold

These earrings are always a favorite.

An elipse shaped Tiffany stone dangles within large 14k gold-fill hand-formed hoops. 

Tiffany stone glows a range of color- it is very similiar in its appearence to opal. It glows various shades of pink, blue, yellow and orange, depending on the light that hits it.

An elegant pair of earrings.

Please note: These earrings are made to order. You will be receiving an identical pair to those shown, but not the actual earrings in the photo.
